Prince Vasfli said no more and his cheeks be- gan to twitch nervously, now on one side, now on the other, giving his face an unpleasant ex- pression which was never to be seen on it in a drawing room. His eyes too seemed strange; at one moment they looked impudently sly and at the next glanced round in alarm.
